%% Training Queue FIFO Sequence Diagram

sequenceDiagram
    actor Alice as 👤 Alice
    actor Bob as 👤 Bob
    participant Q as 📋 TrainingQueue
    participant W as ⚙ Worker
    participant DB as 🗄 Database

    Alice->>Q: enqueue(exp-a)
    Q-->>Alice: position #1
    Bob->>Q: enqueue(exp-b)
    Q-->>Bob: position #2
    Alice->>Q: enqueue(exp-c)
    Q-->>Alice: position #3

    loop FIFO Poll
        W->>Q: poll()
        Q->>W: exp-a ▸ running
        W->>W: sklearn train
        W->>DB: status=completed
        W->>Q: poll()
        Q->>W: exp-b ▸ running
        W->>W: sklearn train
        W->>DB: status=completed
    end

    Note over Q,W: 一次只有一个 training running<br/>asyncio.Lock 保证并发安全
